section.def:
frozen confection factory (冰凍甜點製造廠) means any food business which
                    involves, within the meaning of the Frozen Confections Regulation, the
                    manufacture of any frozen confection;

Frozen Confections Regulation
                        (《冰凍甜點規例》) means the Frozen Confections
                    Regulation (Cap. 132 sub. leg. AC);

milk factory (奶品廠) means any food business which involves, within the meaning of
                    the Milk Regulation, the processing or reconstitution of any milk or milk
                    beverage;

Cremation and Gardens
                        of Remembrance Regulation (《火葬及紀念花園規例》) means the Cremation and Gardens of Remembrance
                    Regulation (Cap. 132 sub. leg. M);

Public Cemeteries Regulation
                        (《公眾墳場規例》) means the Public Cemeteries
                    Regulation (Cap. 132 sub. leg. BI);
